 - subject: A subject line for the e-mail.
 - button_text: Customise the text of the form's "submit" button.
[divider] As mentioned above, it’s possible to add some extra fields to this form. While this should not be used in excess, it is useful for adding one or two extra fields to your contact form. These are added as follows: 
Text Input: text_fieldname="Text Field Label|Optional Default Text"
Select Box: select_fieldname="Select Box Label|key=value,key=value,key=value"
Textarea Input: textarea_fieldname="Textarea Field Label|Optional Default Text|Optional Number of Rows|Optional Number of Columns"
Checkbox Input: checkbox_fieldname="Checkbox Field Label|Value of the Checkbox|Checked By Default"
Radio Button Input: radio_fieldname="Radio Field Label|key=value,key=value,key=value|Optional Default Value"
[divider] [toggle title_open="Contact Form" title_closed="Get the code" hide="yes" border="yes" style="default" excerpt_length="0" include_excerpt_html="no"] 
Examples of each field type in use are shown below.
Default usage: [contact_form]


Text Field default usage: text_telephone="Your Telephone Number|021-555-5555"

Select Box: select_besttime="Best Time To Call|morning=In the Morning,afternoon=In the Afternoon,evening=In the Evening"


Textarea: textarea_additionalnotes="Optional Additional Notes|Place any additional notes here|10|20"

Checkbox Input: checkbox_specialoffers="Subscribe to special offers?|Yes|yes"

* NOTE: Checkbox information will only be included if the checkbox is checked. If not, the opposite is assumed.

Radio Button Input: radio_favouriteanimal="Favourite Animal|cat=Cat,dog=Dog,rabbit=Rabbit|dog"

Full example using the above fields:
[contact_form text_telephone="Your Telephone Number|021-555-5555" select_besttime="Best Time To Call|morning=In the Morning,afternoon=In the Afternoon,evening=In the Evening" textarea_additionalnotes="Optional Additional Notes|Place any additional notes here|10|20" checkbox_specialoffers="Subscribe to special offers?|Yes|yes" radio_favouriteanimal="Favourite Animal|cat=Cat,dog=Dog,rabbit=Rabbit|dog"]
[/toggle] [hr]

A facebook 'Like' button shortcode in template (php) files

[fblike] [toggle title_open="Facebook Like button shortcode" title_closed="Get the code" hide="yes" border="yes" style="default" excerpt_length="0" include_excerpt_html="no"]
Just copy and add this code appropriately in your php files.
<php echo do_shortcode('[fblike]'); >
[/toggle] [hr]

TWITTER SOCIAL BUTTON

Twitter Normal Button

[twitter]
You can easily add a the new Twitter button to your posts so you can share them on Twitter.
Optional arguments:
 - style: "horizontal", "vertical", "none" ("none" hides the counter - default: "horizontal")
 - url: specify URL directly
 - source: username to mention in tweet
 - related: related account
 - hashtag: optional hashtags to include.
 - size: optional size of the button (medium or large).
 - text: optional tweet text (default: title of page)
 - float: none, left, right (default: left)
 - lang: 'fr', 'de', 'es', 'js', 'hi', 'zh-cn', 'pt', 'id', 'hu', 'it', 'da', 'tr',
   'fil', 'ko', 'sv', 'no', 'zh-tw', 'nl', 'ru', 'ja', 'fi', 'msa', 'pl' (default: english)
 - use_post_url: automatically retrieve the URL to the specific post (useful on archive screens)
[divider] [toggle title_open="Twitter Normal Button" title_closed="Get the code" hide="yes" border="yes" style="default" excerpt_length="0" include_excerpt_html="no"] 
[twitter]
[/toggle] [divider]

Twitter Follow Button

[twitter_follow username="templatation"]
You can easily add a Twitter Follow button to your website, to show off your Twitter follower count and encourage visitors to follow you on Twitter
Arguments:
- username: Your Twitter username. This argument is required.

Optional arguments:
 - align: optional alignment of the button within the shortcode DIV tag container
 - count: show follower count (default is empty and true. Set to "false" to disable follower count)
 - float: none, left, right (default: left)
 - language: en, fr, de, it, es, ko, ja (default: english)
 - width: An optional width, in percentage (50%50px) format.
 - align: Used in conjunction with 'width' to align the button within the shortcode container DIV tag.
 - size: Specify the size of the button (medium or large)
 - show_screen_name: Optionally hide the display of your screen name on the button (set to "false").
[divider] [toggle title_open="Twitter Follow Button" title_closed="Get the code" hide="yes" border="yes" style="default" excerpt_length="0" include_excerpt_html="no"] 
[twitter_follow username="templatation"]
[twitter_follow username="templatation" text_color="#CC0033" link_color="#000000" language="de"]
[/toggle] [divider]

Tweetmeme

[tweetmeme]
You can easily add a Tweetmeme button to your posts so you can share them on Twitter.
Optional arguments:
 - link: specify URL directly
 - style: compact
 - source: username
[divider] [toggle title_open="Tweetmeme Button" title_closed="Get the code" hide="yes" border="yes" style="default" excerpt_length="0" include_excerpt_html="no"] 
[tweetmeme"]
[/toggle] [divider] [hr]

DIGG SOCIAL BUTTON

[digg style="medium" float="none"]
Digg buttons are a great way to submit your posts to Digg.com
Optional arguments:
 - link: specify URL directly
 - title: specify a title (must add link also)
 - style: medium, large, compact, icon (default: medium)
 - float: none, left, right (default: left)
[divider] [toggle title_open="Digg Button" title_closed="Get the code" hide="yes" border="yes" style="default" excerpt_length="0" include_excerpt_html="no"] 
[digg style="medium" float="none"]
[/toggle] [hr]

FACEBOOK LIKE

[fblike]
Add a “like” button to your posts so visitors can like your story on FaceBook.
Optional arguments:
 - float: none (default), left, right
 - url: link you want to share (default: current post ID)
 - style: standard (default), button_count
 - showfaces: true or false (default)
 - width: 450
 - verb: like (default) or recommend
 - colorscheme: light (default), dark
 - font: arial (default), lucida grande, segoe ui, tahoma, trebuchet ms, verdana
 - locale: optionally add a locale to change the Facebook button's language (eg: de_DE for German or fr_FR for French)
[divider] [toggle title_open="Facebook Like Button" title_closed="Get the code" hide="yes" border="yes" style="default" excerpt_length="0" include_excerpt_html="no"] 
[fblike]
[/toggle] [divider]

FACEBOOK SHARE

[fbshare]
Add a “share” button to your posts so visitors can share your story on FaceBook.
Optional arguments:
 - type: box_count, button_count, button (default), icon_link, or icon
 - float: none, left, right (default: left)
[divider] [toggle title_open="Facebook Share Button" title_closed="Get the code" hide="yes" border="yes" style="default" excerpt_length="0" include_excerpt_html="no"] 
[fbshare]
[fbshare type="button_count" float="none"]Custom Text[/fbshare]
[/toggle] [hr]

GOOGLE +1

[google_plusone]
Add a "+1" button to your posts so visitors can show their friends that they like a post.
Optional arguments:
 - href: Optional specific URL to "+1". Takes the current URL if no URL is specified
 - size: standard, small, medium, tall
 - float: none, left, right (default: left)
 - annotation: none, bubble, inline (default: none)
 - callback: optional callback JavaScript function to run when the button is clicked
 - language: optionally change the language to one of the following supported languages:
 -- Arabic, Bulgarian, Catalan, Chinese (Simplified), Chinese (Traditional), Croatian, Czech, Danish, Dutch,
English (US), English (UK), Estonian, Filipino, Finnish, French, German, Greek, Hebrew, Hindi, Hungarian,
 Indonesian, Italian, Japanese, Korean, Latvian, Lithuanian, Malay, Norwegian, Persian, Polish,
 Portuguese (Brazil), Portuguese (Portugal), Romanian, Russian, Serbian, Swedish, Slovak, Slovenian,
 Spanish, Spanish (Latin America), Thai, Turkish, Ukrainian, Vietnamese
[divider] [toggle title_open="Google +1 Button" title_closed="Get the code" hide="yes" border="yes" style="default" excerpt_length="0" include_excerpt_html="no"] 
[google_plusone]
[google_plusone size="tall"]
[/toggle] [hr]

STUMBLEUPON BADGE

[stumbleupon]
Add a StumbleUpon badge to your posts so visitors can share your story on StumbleUpon.
Optional arguments:
 - design: The format to use to display the badge (horizontal_large (default), horizontal_medium, horizontal_small, icon_small,
 icon_large, vertical_count)
 - float: The position of the badge (left, right, none (default))
 - url: An optional URL to link to on the badge.
 - use_post: Use the most recent $post variable as the link (useful in archive screens when linking to each individual post).
 Alternatively, the current page URL is used.
[divider] [toggle title_open="StumbleUpon Badge Button" title_closed="Get the code" hide="yes" border="yes" style="default" excerpt_length="0" include_excerpt_html="no"] 
[stumbleupon]
[stumbleupon url="#" float="none" design="icon_large"]
[/toggle] [hr]

PINTEREST “PIN IT” BUTTON

[pinterest]
Add a Pinterest “Pin It” to your posts so visitors can share your posts on Pinterest (featured images required).
Optional arguments:
 - count: The format to use to display the counter (horizontal (default), vertical, none)
 - float: The position of the button (left, right, none (default))
 - url: An optional URL to link to on the button (defaults to current $post URL).
 - image_url: An optional image URL to link to on the button (defaults to current $post's image).
 - use_post: Use the most recent $post variable as the link (useful in archive screens when linking to each individual post).
[divider] [toggle title_open="Pinterest 'Pin It' Button" title_closed="Get the code" hide="yes" border="yes" style="default" excerpt_length="0" include_excerpt_html="no"] 
[pinterest]
[pinterest url="#" design="vertical"]
[/toggle] [hr]

LINKEDIN SHARE BUTTON

[linkedin_share]
Add a LinkedIn share button to your posts so visitors can share your posts on LinkedIn.
Optional arguments:
 - style: The format to use to display the counter (none (default), top, right)
 - float: The position of the button (left, right, none (default))
 - url: An optional URL to link to on the button (defaults to current $post URL).
[divider] [toggle title_open="LinkedIn Share Button" title_closed="Get the code" hide="yes" border="yes" style="default" excerpt_length="0" include_excerpt_html="no"] 

[linkedin_share]
[linkedin_share url="#" style="top"]
[/toggle] [hr]

item.title: Page Templates
item.dc:creator: adminac
item.content:encoded:
[sidenav]
  • Beautifully Designed
  • 3 Layouts
  • FAQ Page
  • Page Templates
  • Powerful Admin
  • SEO Friendly
  • Custom Widgets
  • 404 Page
[/sidenav] [sidenav_content] JustShop comes with 12 custom page template making it possible for you to create the page of your choice in seconds. To use these pages , just create a new page from admin panel and select the desired page template from right side block of selecting page template. The 12 Page template are: [unordered_list style="tick"]
  • Archive
  • Blog
  • Contact us
  • Custom Homepage
  • Image Gallery
  • Full Width
  • Portfolio one col
  • Portfolio two col
  • Portfolio Three col
  • Sitemap
  • Tags
  • Timeline
[/unordered_list]

Archive

Archive page template shows all content of your wordpress website in archive manner. Sorted beautifully by recent and by time. Check out Demo here. [hr]

Blog

Blog page template is just another page template to show blog posts in listing manner. Its almost same as index page , its just has been created to give you more flexibility to have in your blog listing page. Check out Demo here. [hr]

Contact us

Contact us page template creates the contact us page with working contact us form. It also provides a feature of setting up your address and enabling/ disabling social media solution on it. It also incorporates google map on it. You just need to enter your details for contact page in Theme-options -> Contact page settings. Check out Demo here. [hr]

Custom Homepage

Customhomepage page template makes it easy for you to form a homepage. You can activate this page template and manage its content from Theme-options -> Homepage. Check out Demo here. [hr]

Image Gallery

Image gallery template shows images from your blog in a beautiful and simple way. Check out Demo here. [hr]

Full Width

As the name suggest , this is just a page template when you want to have a full page width for some reason. ie you do not want sidebar on given page. For example we have shortcode page full width. Check out Demo here. [hr]

Portfolio one col

This page template shows the portfolio item in 1 column format. This page template also show little intro about portfolios. These portfolio you can create in Portfolio custom post type. Check out Demo here. [hr]

Portfolio two col

This page template shows the portfolio item in 2 column format. Check out Demo here. [hr]

Portfolio Three col

This page template shows the portfolio item in 3 column format. Check out Demo here. [hr]

Sitemap

This page template creates a beautiful human readable Sitemap for your whole website. Archive page template shows all content of your wordpress website in archive manner. Sorted beautifully by recent and by time. Check out Demo here. [hr]

Tags

This page template lists the tags from your whole website. Check out Demo here. [hr]

Timeline

This page template shows the content of the website in a timely sorted manner. Check out Demo here [/sidenav_content]

item.title: Powerful Admin Panel
item.dc:creator: adminac
item.content:encoded:
[sidenav]
  • Beautifully Designed
  • 3 Layouts
  • FAQ Page
  • Page Templates
  • Powerful Admin
  • SEO Friendly
  • Custom Widgets
  • 404 Page
[/sidenav] [sidenav_content] Justshop comes with powerful and robust admin panel. You can control almost all areas of the theme without touching the code. Brief introduction to theme options panel features are given below. [unordered_list style="tick"]
  1. General Settings: This section provides interface for very basic settings like Logo, favicon, Breadcrumb, Custom css, RSS, Analytics code, etc.
  2. Styling: Here you can apply background colors and images. You can also have your choice of colors to links, buttons, etc.
  3. Layout: Here you can decide how you want your 'Main Layout' for your site (i.e. Left sidebar or Right sidebar).
  4. Homepage: This tab setting has 5 sections which help in arranging and customizing the homepage layout with the content you choose to display. Sections are like: 'Product Categories', 'Featured Products', 'About Us', 'Testimonials' and 'Content area'. Most of the setting have easy short descriptions for your to understand and follow.
  5. Portfolio: You can choose to select and display any portfolio gallery you have created if you want it to be 'featured'. Additional settings provide option to link the portfolio item to its 'lightbox' image or its own link.
  6. WooCommerce: This tab has 3 sections to generally choose how and what stuff you like to show up. Note: [You need to have products for this to take effect.]
  7. Footer Customization: Most of the stuff seen in footer of theme can be configured here with options to choose how many footer widget areas you want to display or customize text to display in (left or right) side of footer. There is also a sub-section called 'Extreme footer content' to customize copyright text, etc.
  8. Subscribe and Connect: Here you can add your social networks sharing urls and also enable Feedburner ID for the e-mail subscription form. If you want to enable 'Subscribe and Connect' on single post, there is option to choose that too and more. Note: [You also have option to enable or diable showing the subscribe and RSS icon.]
  9. Contact Page: This section allows you to enter your e-mail address if you want to use it on the 'Contact Form' page Template. You can also apply Google Map coordinates and customize it to display a map on the Contact Form page template and a link to it on the Contact Us widget. Use this site to find co-ordinates
[/unordered_list] [/sidenav_content]

item.title: SEO Friendly
item.dc:creator: adminac
item.content:encoded:
[sidenav]
  • Beautifully Designed
  • 3 Layouts
  • FAQ Page
  • Page Templates
  • Powerful Admin
  • SEO Friendly
  • Custom Widgets
  • 404 Page
[/sidenav] [sidenav_content] Seo(Search Engine Optimization) is vital part for your website and your business. It helps your website to rank higher in search engine which in turns provides you more business. Justshop theme got you covered on seo part. All pages/post/content are laid out nicely with proper heading and paragraph tags, every page has proper meta tags including previous, next... and not to mention products pages has in-built google scheme.org incorporated. Many features like star rating, icons, most of the images uses latest sprite and other latest technologies to make it possible for search spiders to read important content while still making them looking beautiful. As well as the html is cleaner, the non-important objects are plugged in using jquery on run time which loads only for user viewing and not for spiders. [/sidenav_content]

item.title: Beautifully Designed Theme
item.dc:creator: adminac
item.content:encoded:
[sidenav]
  • Beautifully Designed
  • 3 Layouts
  • FAQ Page
  • Page Templates
  • Powerful Admin
  • SEO Friendly
  • Custom Widgets
  • 404 Page
[/sidenav] [sidenav_content] Justshop has been designed beautifully with a clear motive in mind, to make it user friendly along with aesthetics. It provides a pleasant feeling to the user through out the browsing and buying product. It comes with 3 different layouts of header, making it possible to give your website a different look. From advanced theme options panel you can manage/configure many design aspects to make them fit to your specific need. You are welcome to browse few of pages to see the awesomeness of designing in Justshop. [/sidenav_content]

item.title: Sliding Gallery
item.dc:creator: adminac
item.content:encoded: [vc_row][vc_column width="1/1"][vc_message color="alert-danger" style="3d" el_class="noicon"]You can create unlimited image sliders like below ones using the included Revolution Slider plugin. This plugin has many advanced features and we have specially embedded it into Justshop theme to make it work smoothly. We also provide you with ready-made samples of sliders just like this, so all you have to do is put in your big images, set the type (fixed, responsive or full-width) and you are instantly ready to publish. There are many more customizations you can do if you spend a few moments dabbling with its animation settings. Animations and transitions are a breeze to configure within this slider's settings and most of it is very cleanly explained (in the provided help documents) so it becomes absolutely easy for you to quickly get your slider published![/vc_message][vc_separator color="grey" tt_line="yes"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width="1/1"][rev_slider_vc alias="layout3"][/vc_column][/vc_row]

item.title: Full/Boxed width
item.dc:creator: adminac
item.content:encoded:
[vc_row][vc_column width="1/1"][vc_message color="alert-danger" style="3d" el_class="noicon"]
Justshop theme by default has ‘boxed’ layout having 1000px fixed width but enabling Widescreen mode allows you to have a fluid layout. Main container with white background (which has the headline “Full/Boxed width”) will flow horizontally to as much full width available. But nevertheless, your content will still be inside 1000px width visible expanding (or contracting) accordingly on all devices.
[/vc_message][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width="1/1"][vc_single_image image="1916" alignment="center" img_link_target="_self" title="Widescreen Mode Setting" img_size="625x130" border_color="grey" el_class="noborder"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width="1/1"][vc_single_image image="1918" img_link_target="_self" title="Widescreen On" img_size="625x580" alignment="center" border_color="grey"][vc_separator color="grey" tt_line="yes"][vc_single_image image="1917" img_link_target="_self" title="Widescreen Off" img_size="420x480" alignment="center" border_color="grey"][/vc_column][/vc_row]

item.title: Powerful Options Panel
item.dc:creator: adminac
item.content:encoded:
[vc_row][vc_column width="1/1"][vc_message color="alert-success" style="3d" el_class="noicon"]
Justshop comes with an easy to understand and robust theme options panel. Nearly all features of the website can be configured or modified with just a few mouse clicks. We’ve also thought ahead: in the case you want to update or migrate your website, the theme options panel includes an import/export of theme settings.
[/vc_message][vc_single_image image="1828" css_animation="top-to-bottom" img_link_large="yes" img_link_target="_self" title="Justshop Theme Options Panel" img_size="820x750" alignment="center" border_color="grey" el_class="noborder"][/vc_column][/vc_row]

item.title: It is an almost unorthographic life
item.dc:creator: adminac
item.content:encoded:
The Big Oxmox advised her not to do so, because there were thousands of bad Commas, wild Question Marks and devious Semikoli, but the Little Blind Text didn’t listen.
She packed her seven versalia, put her initial into the belt and made herself on the way.
When she reached the first hills of the Italic Mountains, she had a last view back on the skyline of her hometown Bookmarksgrove, the headline of Alphabet Village and the subline of her own road, the Line Lane.
Pityful a rethoric question ran over her cheek, then she continued her way. On her way she met a copy.

item.title: Incapable of drawing a single stroke at the present moment
item.dc:creator: adminac
item.content:encoded:
O my friend -- but it is too much for my strength -- I sink under the weight of the splendour of these visions!
A wonderful serenity has taken possession of my entire soul, like these sweet mornings of spring which I enjoy with my whole heart.
I am alone, and feel the charm of existence in this spot, which was created for the bliss of souls like mine.

item.title: A few stray gleams steal into the inner sanctuary
item.dc:creator: adminac
item.content:encoded:
When, while the lovely valley teems with vapour around me, and the meridian sun strikes the upper surface of the impenetrable foliage of my trees, and but a few stray gleams steal into the inner sanctuary, I throw myself down among the tall grass by the trickling stream.
As I lie close to the earth, a thousand unknown plants are noticed by me: when I hear the buzz of the little world among the stalks, and grow familiar with the countless indescribable forms of the insects and flies

item.title: Regular Updations
item.dc:creator: adminac
item.content:encoded: [vc_row][vc_column width="1/1"][vc_message color="alert-info" style="3d" el_class="noicon"]When you buy JustShop theme, you are not locked in with those features which you see when you buy the theme. JustShop theme is regularly updated with brand new useful features you'll love and will have latest trends included in its core but you have the freedom to choose to use whichever suits your purpose.[/vc_message][bsf-info-box icon_type="selector" icon="Defaults-refresh" img_width="48" icon_size="32" icon_color="#ffffff" icon_style="circle" icon_color_bg="#dd3333" icon_color_border="#333333" icon_border_size="1" icon_border_radius="500" icon_border_spacing="50" title="Stay Updated / Up-to-date all the time" read_more="none" read_text="Read More" hover_effect="style_1" pos="top"][/bsf-info-box][vc_column_text]We promise Justshop theme will be made compatible with new versions of WordPress that comes out in future! Feel free to use it on your clients project with confidence, you won't have to fix when things break when WordPress updates in future. You can future-proof your theme updates because we supply a child theme in the Download package so that you can update theme easily with 1-click in future. Still not yet convinced? Please feel free to check out updates list here to make sure that we have actually done that previously rather than listening to our boasting above :-)[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row]

item.title: A wonderful serenity has taken possession of my entire soul
item.dc:creator: adminac
item.content:encoded: [caption id="attachment_26" align="alignright" width="210"] Wonderful serenity[/caption] [dropcap]W[/dropcap]hen, while the lovely valley teems with vapour around me, and the meridian sun strikes the upper surface of the impenetrable foliage of my trees, and but a few stray gleams steal into the inner sanctuary, I throw myself down among the tall grass by the trickling stream; and, as I lie close to the earth, a thousand unknown plants are noticed by me: when I hear the buzz of the little world among the stalks, and grow familiar with the countless indescribable forms of the insects and flies Then I feel the presence of the Almighty, who formed us in his own image, and the breath of that universal love which bears and sustains us, as it floats around us in an eternity of bliss And then, my friend, when darkness overspreads my eyes, and heaven and earth seem to dwell in my soul and absorb its power, like the form of a beloved mistress, then I often think with longing. Oh, would I could describe these conceptions, could impress upon paper all that is living so full and warm within me, that it might be the mirror of my soul, as my soul is the mirror of the infinite God!

item.title: Doing business like this takes much more effort than doing your own business at home
item.dc:creator: adminac
item.content:encoded:
The bedding was hardly able to cover it and seemed ready to slide off any moment. His many legs, pitifully thin compared with the size of the rest of him, waved about helplessly as he looked. [quote style="boxed" float="right"] "What's happened to me?"[/quote] he thought. It wasn't a dream. His room, a proper human room although a little too small, lay peacefully between its four familiar walls.
A collection of textile samples lay spread out on the table - Samsa was a travelling salesman - and above it there hung a picture that he had recently cut out of an illustrated magazine and housed in a nice, gilded frame.
It showed a lady fitted out with a fur hat and fur boa who sat upright, raising a heavy fur muff that covered the whole of her lower arm towards the viewer. Gregor then turned to look out the window at the dull weather.
[highlight]Drops of rain[/highlight] could be heard hitting the pane, which made him feel quite sad.
"How about if I sleep a little bit longer and forget all this nonsense", he thought, but that was something he was unable to do because he was used to sleeping on his right, and in his present state couldn't get into that position.
